1
00:01:48,040 --> 00:01:48,560
Zhou Wan.

2
00:01:52,000 --> 00:01:52,879
Thanks for today.

3
00:01:53,719 --> 00:01:54,359
Good night.

4
00:01:57,840 --> 00:01:58,439
Good night.

5
00:02:19,319 --> 00:02:20,919
You've lived here a while now.

6
00:02:21,520 --> 00:02:22,639
Getting used to it?

7
00:02:26,400 --> 00:02:27,639
How's Grandma?

8
00:02:33,240 --> 00:02:34,400
I've set aside

9
00:02:34,400 --> 00:02:35,560
the rest of the money.

10
00:02:38,800 --> 00:02:39,599
Also,

11
00:02:39,879 --> 00:02:41,240
I asked around for you.

12
00:02:41,719 --> 00:02:42,879
About the kidney donor,

13
00:02:43,240 --> 00:02:45,039
