14
00:02:46,360 --> 00:02:47,000
See?

15
00:02:48,319 --> 00:02:49,599
Everything I promised you,

16
00:02:50,120 --> 00:02:51,319
I've delivered.

17
00:02:53,360 --> 00:02:54,000
