Zhou Wan, I'm coming in.

22
00:03:11,800 --> 00:03:12,680
What are you doing here?

23
00:03:12,919 --> 00:03:13,680
Nothing.

24
00:03:14,039 --> 00:03:15,439
You two got back so late.

25
00:03:15,439 --> 00:03:16,639
I just wanted to check on her.

26
00:03:17,000 --> 00:03:18,039
Get some rest.

27
00:03:18,319 --> 00:03:19,319
Don't stay up.

28
00:03:19,919 --> 00:03:20,759
Off to bed now.

29
00:03:21,840 --> 00:03:22,560
Night.

30
00:03:33,159 --> 00:03:35,120
Forgot to give you this.

31
00:03:36,840 --> 00:03:37,520
For me?

32
00:03:40,000 --> 00:03:42,520
What about Professor Qin?

33
00:03:43,159 --> 00:03:44,719
This one's not for him anyway.

34
00:03:45,080 --> 00:03:45,919
It's for you.

35
00:03:50,039 --> 00:03:51,000
You drew this for me?

36
00:03:52,479 --> 00:03:53,000
Come on.

37
00:03:53,000 --> 00:03:54,520
It's no big deal.

38
00:03:55,840 --> 00:03:56,960
What did she just say to you?

39
00:03:59,439 --> 00:04:00,319
Nothing really.

40
00:04:01,560 --> 00:04:03,080
Just said

41
00:04:03,080 --> 00:04:04,719
I haven't been studying much lately,

42
00:04:04,960 --> 00:04:06,159
just checking up on me.

43
00:04:07,960 --> 00:04:08,800
Did she give you a hard time?

44
00:04:09,240 --> 00:04:11,879
No. She's my sponsor,

45
00:04:12,639 --> 00:04:13,479
why would she?

46
00:04:17,240 --> 00:04:19,279
Haven't gotten to study properly lately.

47
00:04:20,560 --> 00:04:21,439
I'm gonna study for a while,

48
00:04:21,639 --> 00:04:22,680
you go back and rest.

49
00:04:24,639 --> 00:04:25,240
Alright.

50
00:04:26,279 --> 00:04:27,079
Sleep well.

51
00:04:29,879 --> 00:04:30,439
Oh right,

52
00:04:31,439 --> 00:04:33,279
Jiang Fan wants us to hang out tomorrow.

53
00:04:33,680 --> 00:04:34,759
You head over first,

54
00:04:35,079 --> 00:04:35,680
I need to sort out

55
00:04:35,680 --> 00:04:36,759
the drawings for the professor.

56
00:04:38,079 --> 00:04:38,720
Okay.

57
00:05:23,439 --> 00:05:24,480
He heard everything?

58
00:05:24,720 --> 00:05:25,439
He didn't.

59
00:05:25,879 --> 00:05:27,040
Why did he come to see you?

60
00:05:30,439 --> 00:05:31,480
It's none of your business.

61
00:05:33,600 --> 00:05:34,720
I have a feeling

62
00:05:35,879 --> 00:05:37,319
you've got a crush on Lu Xixiao.

63
00:05:38,560 --> 00:05:40,680
You look more nervous than I am.

64
00:05:43,879 --> 00:05:44,879
No wonder.

65
00:05:45,160 --> 00:05:46,279
You like him,

66
00:05:47,000 --> 00:05:48,519
that's why you're always opposing me.

67
00:05:50,560 --> 00:05:51,560
I advise you

68
00:05:52,120 --> 00:05:53,879
to send him away for good.

69
00:06:04,279 --> 00:06:05,160
Don't come any closer.

70
00:06:05,680 --> 00:06:07,000
Or I'll tear it up.

71
00:06:07,399 --> 00:06:08,240
Who drew this?

72
00:06:09,319 --> 00:06:10,120
Answer me.

73
00:06:11,040 --> 00:06:11,920
He did.

74
00:06:12,560 --> 00:06:13,360
What's it for?

75
00:06:17,279 --> 00:06:17,920
It's

76
00:06:19,399 --> 00:06:20,519
for Professor Qin.

77
00:06:23,439 --> 00:06:24,639
You've got some nerve.

78
00:06:43,000 --> 00:06:43,800
Just tell him Ms. Chen

79
00:06:43,800 --> 00:06:45,040
tossed it by accident.

80
00:07:29,959 --> 00:07:31,399
Are these skewers done?

81
00:07:34,560 --> 00:07:36,759
What's wrong? You seem distracted.

82
00:07:38,600 --> 00:07:39,480
I'm fine.

83
00:07:39,560 --> 00:07:40,319
No, you're not.

84
00:07:40,920 --> 00:07:42,279
Probably just worn out lately.

85
00:07:45,639 --> 00:07:47,199
After that night,

86
00:07:47,959 --> 00:07:48,879
did you two get together?

87
00:07:49,560 --> 00:07:50,480
No.

88
00:07:50,920 --> 00:07:52,360
He's so impulsive.

89
00:07:52,360 --> 00:07:53,759
Why date him just 'cause he confessed?

90
00:07:54,000 --> 00:07:55,439
That'll be long-distance.

91
00:07:55,800 --> 00:07:56,360
He owes me a plan for

92
00:07:56,360 --> 00:07:57,240
how we'll make this work.

93
00:07:59,000 --> 00:08:00,000
So you didn't turn him down?

94
00:08:01,000 --> 00:08:03,120
I do like him,

95
00:08:03,120 --> 00:08:04,000
a tiny bit.

96
00:08:04,160 --> 00:08:05,600
But I can't just go along with his whims.

97
00:08:06,959 --> 00:08:08,199
Only a tiny bit?

98
00:08:09,079 --> 00:08:09,879
Yeah.

99
00:08:15,600 --> 00:08:17,279
What's it like getting confessed to?

100
00:08:18,279 --> 00:08:20,120
Why do you wanna know that?

101
00:08:20,519 --> 00:08:21,800
I'm only human, after all.

102
00:08:22,360 --> 00:08:23,680
Everyone gets silly

103
00:08:23,680 --> 00:08:25,199
when they're crushing on someone.

104
00:08:25,360 --> 00:08:26,399
Didn't I tell you? Your body reacts

105
00:08:26,600 --> 00:08:29,120
before your brain when you like someone.

106
00:08:32,320 --> 00:08:33,600
What nonsense.

107
00:08:34,080 --> 00:08:35,879
What "body reacts before the brain"?

108
00:08:36,840 --> 00:08:38,279
Were you eavesdropping on us?

109
00:08:38,559 --> 00:08:40,519
It means I didn't think it through.

110
00:08:40,519 --> 00:08:42,120
- I just...
- I came for the skewers.

111
00:08:42,120 --> 00:08:43,840
I wasn't eavesdropping.

112
00:08:44,200 --> 00:08:45,080
I want some of this

113
00:08:45,080 --> 00:08:45,919
and just happened to walk by.

114
00:08:48,279 --> 00:08:50,080
Watch out, don't bump into him.

115
00:08:50,080 --> 00:08:51,159
Stop messing around, okay?

116
00:08:58,600 --> 00:08:59,320
I want this one.

117
00:09:00,240 --> 00:09:01,720
It's alcohol. It's not for kids.

118
00:09:02,279 --> 00:09:04,440
I'm not a kid,

119
00:09:04,440 --> 00:09:05,480
I'm an adult now.

120
00:09:11,000 --> 00:09:11,639
Thanks.

121
00:09:14,000 --> 00:09:14,679
What for?

122
00:09:16,039 --> 00:09:17,320
The drawing I gave you.

123
00:09:18,120 --> 00:09:19,480
I couldn't have finished it without you.

124
00:09:20,759 --> 00:09:21,399
You like it?

125
00:09:26,799 --> 00:09:27,480
Yeah.

126
00:09:29,000 --> 00:09:29,840
Glad you do.

127
00:09:37,039 --> 00:09:38,480
What does being drunk feel like?

128
00:09:40,919 --> 00:09:41,799
Nothing special.

129
00:09:43,519 --> 00:09:44,799
You just get wasted.

130
00:09:45,879 --> 00:09:46,799
Once drunk,

131
00:09:47,200 --> 00:09:48,519
all joys and sorrows fade away.

132
00:09:50,960 --> 00:09:51,879
We've got enough skewers.

133
00:09:51,879 --> 00:09:53,600
Stop grilling, come hang inside.

134
00:09:55,120 --> 00:09:56,399
Go inside, I'll handle the grill.

135
00:10:07,039 --> 00:10:08,559
Need me to take over?

136
00:10:10,559 --> 00:10:11,799
Just take a seat.

137
00:10:11,799 --> 00:10:12,600
I've got this.

138
00:10:15,240 --> 00:10:15,919
Wanna try some?

139
00:10:17,759 --> 00:10:18,600
For me?

140
00:10:19,639 --> 00:10:20,440
You're eighteen now.

141
00:10:20,440 --> 00:10:21,440
It's fine to have a sip.

142
00:10:33,080 --> 00:10:34,240
Don't tell anyone I gave this to you.

143
00:10:35,919 --> 00:10:36,960
It's so good.

144
00:10:37,320 --> 00:10:38,000
Of course.

145
00:10:43,799 --> 00:10:44,600
Ms. Chen,

146
00:10:44,639 --> 00:10:46,360
these two silk garments

147
00:10:46,440 --> 00:10:47,320
need hand-washing.

148
00:10:47,440 --> 00:10:47,879
Got it.

149
00:10:49,879 --> 00:10:50,600
This is...

150
00:10:51,759 --> 00:10:52,679
Xixiao's.

151
00:10:53,799 --> 00:10:54,960
Where'd he go?

152
00:10:56,360 --> 00:10:57,720
I don't know.

153
00:10:58,879 --> 00:11:01,000
Wan went with him?

154
00:11:03,919 --> 00:11:04,639
That's good.

155
00:11:04,960 --> 00:11:06,840
He's usually a loner.

156
00:11:06,919 --> 00:11:07,799
But ever since Wan came,

157
00:11:07,840 --> 00:11:09,000
he's got someone to keep him company.

158
00:11:09,679 --> 00:11:10,279
Yeah.

159
00:11:12,200 --> 00:11:12,799
Off you go.

160
00:11:16,200 --> 00:11:16,879
Zhou Wan,

161
00:11:17,240 --> 00:11:18,279
you lied to me.

162
00:12:18,360 --> 00:12:19,399
So pretty.

163
00:12:28,159 --> 00:12:30,759
One, two, three, four, five.

164
00:12:30,960 --> 00:12:33,200
Follow your...

165
00:12:35,360 --> 00:12:38,360
One, two, three, four, five.

166
00:12:38,679 --> 00:12:39,759
One, two, three, four, five.

167
00:12:39,759 --> 00:12:40,679
She's drunk, isn't she?

168
00:12:42,200 --> 00:12:43,039
Who gave her alcohol?

169
00:12:44,360 --> 00:12:46,480
Who gave her alcohol?

170
00:12:46,480 --> 00:12:48,440
One, two, three, four, five.

171
00:12:48,679 --> 00:12:49,159
Let's...

172
00:12:49,159 --> 00:12:50,240
You've been drinking, right?

173
00:12:50,360 --> 00:12:51,240
Did you drink?

174
00:12:51,840 --> 00:12:52,799
You gave it to her, didn't you?

175
00:12:53,000 --> 00:12:53,720
You did it?

176
00:12:54,480 --> 00:12:55,320
Ping, you gave it to her?

177
00:12:55,320 --> 00:12:55,840
Didn't you?

178
00:12:55,840 --> 00:12:57,440
Not me. I had gloves on.

179
00:12:59,519 --> 00:13:00,279
Let's sing together.

180
00:13:04,360 --> 00:13:05,399
I picked this song,

181
00:13:05,399 --> 00:13:06,440
but I don't know how to sing it.

182
00:13:06,519 --> 00:13:07,279
Here, take the mic.

183
00:13:07,279 --> 00:13:08,120
How does this song go?

184
00:13:19,840 --> 00:13:20,840
It hurts.

185
00:13:27,600 --> 00:13:28,559
Lu Xixiao,

186
00:13:29,200 --> 00:13:30,279
my leg hurts.

187
00:13:48,360 --> 00:13:49,159
This one?

188
00:13:54,799 --> 00:13:55,759
Or this one?

189
00:14:44,000 --> 00:14:44,879
You're totally drunk.

190
00:14:48,120 --> 00:14:49,600
My head's just spinning.

191
00:14:52,919 --> 00:14:53,639
Why'd you

192
00:14:53,639 --> 00:14:55,039
drink so much anyway?

193
00:14:59,200 --> 00:15:00,720
Because I'm kind of sad.

194
00:15:03,320 --> 00:15:04,080
What's making you sad?

195
00:15:08,120 --> 00:15:09,679
I did something terrible.

196
00:15:11,799 --> 00:15:12,799
I regret it so much.

197
00:15:15,080 --> 00:15:17,000
But I don't think I can turn back now.

198
00:15:20,759 --> 00:15:21,759
It's like

199
00:15:23,480 --> 00:15:24,960
I sacrificed everything

200
00:15:26,960 --> 00:15:28,200
just for one single thing.

201
00:15:33,879 --> 00:15:35,440
I even turned into a bad person.

202
00:15:37,960 --> 00:15:38,759
But in the end,

203
00:15:38,759 --> 00:15:39,799
I might gain nothing,

204
00:15:41,320 --> 00:15:42,879
and fix nothing at all.

205
00:15:46,480 --> 00:15:47,679
The only thing that changed

206
00:15:50,879 --> 00:15:52,200
is that I've gone rotten.

207
00:15:53,639 --> 00:15:54,919
So what if you're bad?

208
00:15:59,120 --> 00:16:00,519
Don't you hate bad people?

209
00:16:02,360 --> 00:16:03,639
I'm not a good person anyway.

210
00:16:10,480 --> 00:16:11,320
You are a good one.

211
00:16:18,399 --> 00:16:19,279
Lu Xixiao,

212
00:16:20,000 --> 00:16:21,360
you might not realize it,

213
00:16:22,320 --> 00:16:23,759
but you're honest,

214
00:16:24,440 --> 00:16:25,480
kind,

215
00:16:27,840 --> 00:16:28,679
and gentle.

216
00:16:30,679 --> 00:16:31,240
No matter what,

217
00:16:31,240 --> 00:16:32,480
you could never be bad.

218
00:16:34,960 --> 00:16:36,399
Then you have terrible taste in people.

219
00:16:38,720 --> 00:16:39,720
No way.

220
00:16:40,480 --> 00:16:42,120
Everyone I care about is good.

221
00:16:45,159 --> 00:16:46,000
You,

222
00:16:48,159 --> 00:16:49,039
Gu Meng,

223
00:16:50,840 --> 00:16:52,840
you're all such wonderful people.

224
00:16:54,679 --> 00:16:55,879
I adore you all so much.

225
00:17:05,799 --> 00:17:06,880
Talking about this

226
00:17:09,599 --> 00:17:10,720
makes me sad again.

227
00:17:16,359 --> 00:17:17,960
I'm not a kind person.

228
00:17:20,240 --> 00:17:21,599
That's why I wanna treat you well.

229
00:17:24,160 --> 00:17:25,200
If I'm good to you,

230
00:17:27,000 --> 00:17:28,319
does that make up for

231
00:17:28,519 --> 00:17:30,200
some of my mistakes?

232
00:17:34,599 --> 00:17:35,720
Then maybe I'm not

233
00:17:35,720 --> 00:17:36,759
completely awful.

234
00:18:35,839 --> 00:18:38,279
Wan, it's okay even if you're flawed.

235
00:18:38,839 --> 00:18:40,279
Someone will love every version of you.

236
00:18:58,160 --> 00:18:58,960
Lu Xixiao.

237
00:19:04,400 --> 00:19:05,680
Did you bring your portfolio?

238
00:19:06,880 --> 00:19:08,039
Did you bring your portfolio?

239
00:19:08,480 --> 00:19:09,000
Yeah.

240
00:19:10,200 --> 00:19:11,240
You'll definitely pass.

241
00:19:14,039 --> 00:19:14,599
What?

242
00:19:15,920 --> 00:19:17,079
You'll definitely pass.

243
00:19:17,240 --> 00:19:18,759
Speak up, I can't hear you.

244
00:19:20,079 --> 00:19:21,319
You'll definitely pass.

245
00:19:29,200 --> 00:19:29,759
Bye.

246
00:19:49,960 --> 00:19:50,599
Wan.

247
00:19:51,720 --> 00:19:52,680
Come take a look.

248
00:19:53,519 --> 00:19:55,079
Aren't these flowers beautiful?

249
00:19:56,039 --> 00:19:57,640
Would they suit my wedding?

250
00:19:59,599 --> 00:20:00,519
As long as you're happy.

251
00:20:01,759 --> 00:20:03,400
Is that how you talk to your elders?

252
00:20:04,480 --> 00:20:05,119
Come here.

253
00:20:06,279 --> 00:20:07,400
I need to talk to you.

254
00:20:09,559 --> 00:20:10,240
What's up?

255
00:20:11,000 --> 00:20:12,160
You aren't gonna invite me

256
00:20:12,160 --> 00:20:13,279
to your wedding, are you?

257
00:20:15,720 --> 00:20:16,519
Nah.

258
00:20:17,559 --> 00:20:18,720
Our deal

259
00:20:19,000 --> 00:20:20,160
is off.

260
00:20:20,880 --> 00:20:22,480
You can move out of here now.

261
00:20:26,599 --> 00:20:27,440
What did you do?

262
00:20:29,559 --> 00:20:30,720
What did I do?

263
00:20:33,119 --> 00:20:34,880
I just finished

264
00:20:35,279 --> 00:20:36,279
what you were supposed to do.

265
00:20:47,359 --> 00:20:48,319
What did you do to the portfolio?

266
00:20:50,200 --> 00:20:50,920
Isn't it lovely?

267
00:21:00,440 --> 00:21:01,119
Zhou Wan.

268
00:21:02,039 --> 00:21:02,759
Stop wasting your time

269
00:21:02,759 --> 00:21:03,680
on the Lu family.

270
00:21:04,000 --> 00:21:05,079
Focus on your studies.

271
00:21:05,400 --> 00:21:06,920
Let's both live our own lives.

272
00:21:07,519 --> 00:21:08,680
If the portfolio's gone,

273
00:21:08,680 --> 00:21:09,480
Lu Xixiao will know

274
00:21:09,480 --> 00:21:10,160
it was you.

275
00:21:12,160 --> 00:21:12,880
You wouldn't dare.

276
00:21:14,240 --> 00:21:15,200
What are you trying to do?

277
00:21:15,480 --> 00:21:16,559
You swapped his portfolio.

278
00:21:21,480 --> 00:21:22,759
You want him to blame me.

279
00:21:36,920 --> 00:21:37,640
Stop.

280
00:21:38,279 --> 00:21:39,359
If you step out that door,

281
00:21:39,680 --> 00:21:40,720
don't expect any more money.

282
00:21:41,440 --> 00:21:42,960
Let go. I don't want your money anymore.

283
00:21:43,440 --> 00:21:44,079
Guo Yan,

284
00:21:44,640 --> 00:21:45,920
our deal is over.

285
00:21:47,279 --> 00:21:48,519
Starting today,

286
00:21:48,720 --> 00:21:49,559
leave Grandma

287
00:21:49,559 --> 00:21:50,720
and me alone.

288
00:21:51,000 --> 00:21:52,359
And stay away from Lu Xixiao.

289
00:21:56,200 --> 00:21:57,279
If you try to stop me,

290
00:21:57,920 --> 00:21:59,240
I'll expose everything,

291
00:22:00,839 --> 00:22:02,000
and drag you down with me.

292
00:22:27,880 --> 00:22:29,240
What's the hold-up?

293
00:22:29,559 --> 00:22:31,400
Don't know.

294
00:22:31,400 --> 00:22:33,240
Probably an accident up ahead.

295
00:22:35,519 --> 00:22:36,799
Drop me off here, thanks.

296
00:22:39,839 --> 00:22:40,359
Hey.

297
00:22:46,319 --> 00:22:47,839
My car won't start.

298
00:22:47,839 --> 00:22:48,720
Fix it for me right now.

299
00:22:48,920 --> 00:22:49,680
Hurry up and fix it.

300
00:22:50,519 --> 00:22:51,240
See for yourself.

301
00:22:51,359 --> 00:22:52,319
My car won't start.

302
00:23:19,279 --> 00:23:20,119
Professor.

303
00:23:20,960 --> 00:23:21,920
- You're...
- Sorry to bother you.

304
00:23:21,920 --> 00:23:22,720
Sorry.

305
00:23:22,960 --> 00:23:23,480
I'm here to deliver

306
00:23:23,480 --> 00:23:24,680
Lu Xixiao's portfolio.

307
00:23:24,960 --> 00:23:26,319
There was a family issue.

308
00:23:26,640 --> 00:23:27,359
He grabbed the wrong one

309
00:23:27,359 --> 00:23:28,240
when he left.

310
00:23:28,480 --> 00:23:29,920
But he put a lot of effort into this.

311
00:23:30,200 --> 00:23:30,799
Please take a look.

312
00:23:41,799 --> 00:23:42,920
I'm sure you can tell

313
00:23:42,920 --> 00:23:43,880
his mindset this time

314
00:23:44,319 --> 00:23:45,759
is different from

315
00:23:46,000 --> 00:23:47,240
last time.

316
00:23:47,880 --> 00:23:49,200
He really wants to keep drawing.

317
00:23:50,799 --> 00:23:52,559
Could you give him another chance?

318
00:23:52,799 --> 00:23:53,839
Don't turn him down straight away.

319
00:23:55,440 --> 00:23:56,640
The pieces are quite good,

320
00:23:57,119 --> 00:23:59,160
but many areas

321
00:23:59,160 --> 00:24:00,319
lack depth,

322
00:24:00,920 --> 00:24:01,880
I'll go over

323
00:24:02,599 --> 00:24:03,440
these flaws with him

324
00:24:03,440 --> 00:24:04,640
once he's out.

325
00:24:05,720 --> 00:24:08,240
Out? Where'd he go?

326
00:24:08,680 --> 00:24:10,839
I haven't seen the pieces he brought.

327
00:24:11,200 --> 00:24:12,160
He asked

328
00:24:12,160 --> 00:24:13,200
if he could draw live

329
00:24:13,400 --> 00:24:14,680
and let me critique it.

330
00:24:15,119 --> 00:24:16,720
I wanted to see

331
00:24:16,720 --> 00:24:18,079
his live creativity

332
00:24:18,079 --> 00:24:19,119
and attention to detail

333
00:24:19,279 --> 00:24:20,480
before discussing further.

334
00:24:21,440 --> 00:24:22,160
Turns out

335
00:24:22,400 --> 00:24:23,799
he's actually

336
00:24:23,839 --> 00:24:24,720
full of creative inspiration.

337
00:24:24,799 --> 00:24:26,839
So you haven't rejected him?

338
00:24:27,440 --> 00:24:28,240
Not yet.

339
00:24:29,319 --> 00:24:30,039
I thought

340
00:24:30,799 --> 00:24:32,519
I'd decide after he finishes drawing.

341
00:24:33,200 --> 00:24:34,319
Great. Thank you.

342
00:24:35,720 --> 00:24:37,319
He should be out soon.

343
00:24:37,599 --> 00:24:39,079
Would you like to wait for him?

344
00:24:40,640 --> 00:24:42,279
I have other things to do.

345
00:24:43,160 --> 00:24:44,400
I won't intrude any longer.

346
00:24:45,119 --> 00:24:45,640
Alright.

347
00:24:48,119 --> 00:24:49,599
Your technique's great,

348
00:24:50,720 --> 00:24:53,559
and your emotions really shine through,

349
00:24:54,960 --> 00:24:57,599
but some parts are over the top.

350
00:24:59,039 --> 00:25:00,640
Learn to tone it down.

351
00:25:02,720 --> 00:25:05,079
This piece feels rushed and frantic.

352
00:25:10,160 --> 00:25:11,000
Understood.

353
00:25:14,319 --> 00:25:15,200
Still, thank you

354
00:25:16,160 --> 00:25:17,720
for giving me this shot, Professor.

355
00:25:20,599 --> 00:25:22,400
Maybe it was the time pressure today.

356
00:25:22,640 --> 00:25:24,400
You couldn't show your full potential.

357
00:25:24,720 --> 00:25:25,200
But your portfolio

358
00:25:25,200 --> 00:25:27,079
carries far richer

359
00:25:27,359 --> 00:25:28,599
emotional depth.

360
00:25:29,920 --> 00:25:31,200
You've looked through my portfolio?

361
00:25:31,839 --> 00:25:33,400
I'd planned to check it later,

362
00:25:33,599 --> 00:25:35,079
but you'd grabbed the wrong folder.

363
00:25:35,599 --> 00:25:36,960
Someone rushed over

364
00:25:36,960 --> 00:25:38,000
to drop it off for you.

365
00:25:38,359 --> 00:25:39,000
Who was it?

366
00:25:39,799 --> 00:25:40,799
A young girl.

367
00:25:41,240 --> 00:25:43,000
Thin and small-framed.

368
00:25:43,079 --> 00:25:44,279
She left right after.

369
00:25:53,680 --> 00:25:54,319
Where'd she go?

370
00:25:56,039 --> 00:25:57,079
She mentioned this morning

371
00:25:57,079 --> 00:25:58,160
she was visiting her grandma.

372
00:25:58,319 --> 00:26:00,200
She's probably still at the hospital.

373
00:26:00,759 --> 00:26:01,359
Wait.

374
00:26:02,519 --> 00:26:03,319
What's this?

375
00:26:03,599 --> 00:26:04,880
Found it on her desk.

376
00:26:05,279 --> 00:26:07,000
It's torn to shreds.

377
00:26:29,200 --> 00:26:30,200
Didn't know

378
00:26:30,200 --> 00:26:31,559
you're into crafts.

379
00:26:31,559 --> 00:26:32,599
Could you knock before coming in?

380
00:26:32,759 --> 00:26:33,440
Didn't wanna interrupt

381
00:26:33,440 --> 00:26:34,559
your creative flow.

382
00:26:53,000 --> 00:26:53,880
Well, well.

383
00:26:53,880 --> 00:26:55,599
A living thing in your room. That's rare.

384
00:26:58,359 --> 00:26:59,440
I mean that potted flower.

385
00:27:03,319 --> 00:27:04,119
I looked into

386
00:27:04,119 --> 00:27:05,119
what you asked about.

387
00:27:05,559 --> 00:27:07,079
Guo Xiangling was married before.

388
00:27:07,319 --> 00:27:08,799
She didn't lie about that part.

389
00:27:10,720 --> 00:27:12,759
But she also has a daughter.

390
00:27:13,920 --> 00:27:15,640
Your good classmate.

391
00:27:16,000 --> 00:27:16,799
Zhou Wan.

392
00:27:20,720 --> 00:27:21,519
What?

393
00:27:23,519 --> 00:27:24,480
Zhou Wan

394
00:27:24,480 --> 00:27:26,519
is Guo Xiangling's biological daughter.

395
00:27:30,680 --> 00:27:31,440
Gotta say,

396
00:27:31,440 --> 00:27:33,039
those two are so calculating.

397
00:27:33,240 --> 00:27:35,039
They're scheming their way

398
00:27:35,240 --> 00:27:36,759
into our family.

399
00:27:37,519 --> 00:27:38,400
One wrong move,

400
00:27:38,400 --> 00:27:39,480
and both you and your dad

401
00:27:39,519 --> 00:27:41,720
would've fallen right into their trap.

402
00:27:50,319 --> 00:27:51,240
She's not like that.

403
00:27:52,920 --> 00:27:54,000
Not like that?

404
00:27:55,519 --> 00:27:57,400
Then why did she lie to you?

405
00:27:57,400 --> 00:27:58,519
God knows what schemes

406
00:27:58,519 --> 00:27:59,279
she's plotting with Guo Xiangling.

407
00:28:01,759 --> 00:28:03,240
This coffee's terrible.

408
00:28:04,160 --> 00:28:05,599
I'll get you some good beans later.

409
00:28:06,039 --> 00:28:06,559
See ya.

410
00:28:22,240 --> 00:28:22,880
Zhou Wan.

411
00:28:23,920 --> 00:28:24,319
So this is

412
00:28:24,319 --> 00:28:25,680
the secret you've been hiding?

413
00:28:27,240 --> 00:28:28,359
Then why'd you help me today

414
00:28:28,359 --> 00:28:29,440
and deliver my portfolio?

415
00:29:01,039 --> 00:29:03,039
Dr. Chen, you're still working?

416
00:29:03,440 --> 00:29:04,079
Wan.

417
00:29:04,960 --> 00:29:06,240
Good news.

418
00:29:07,039 --> 00:29:08,319
The surgery is scheduled.

419
00:29:10,400 --> 00:29:11,440
Thank you so much, Dr. Chen.

420
00:29:11,440 --> 00:29:12,640
- It's my job, don't mention it.
- Thank you.

421
00:29:13,000 --> 00:29:13,480
Thank you so much.

422
00:29:13,480 --> 00:29:14,680
But we need

423
00:29:14,680 --> 00:29:16,119
a partial payment upfront.

424
00:29:16,440 --> 00:29:17,839
If you're free,

425
00:29:18,079 --> 00:29:18,960
come finish the paperwork

426
00:29:18,960 --> 00:29:20,440
tomorrow or the day after.

427
00:29:21,000 --> 00:29:21,960
I know

428
00:29:22,000 --> 00:29:23,720
this sum might be a real burden

429
00:29:24,079 --> 00:29:25,279
for your family.

430
00:29:25,799 --> 00:29:26,519
It's okay.

431
00:29:27,640 --> 00:29:28,680
I've already planned for it.

432
00:29:29,960 --> 00:29:31,319
If you can't cover it,

433
00:29:31,319 --> 00:29:32,200
just let me know.

434
00:29:32,559 --> 00:29:34,279
We can adjust the plan

435
00:29:34,519 --> 00:29:35,279
and switch back

436
00:29:35,400 --> 00:29:36,559
to conservative treatment.

437
00:29:39,240 --> 00:29:39,799
If we stick with

438
00:29:39,799 --> 00:29:41,400
the current treatment plan,

439
00:29:43,640 --> 00:29:44,640
how many more years

440
00:29:46,920 --> 00:29:48,680
will Grandma have left with me...

441
00:30:03,160 --> 00:30:04,440
The surgery has to happen.

442
00:30:12,720 --> 00:30:14,519
You only need to

443
00:30:14,519 --> 00:30:15,519
sign the loan contract.

444
00:30:16,240 --> 00:30:16,920
Mr. Fang.

445
00:30:17,039 --> 00:30:18,240
This is the payment Luo He

446
00:30:18,240 --> 00:30:19,039
collected last month.

447
00:30:23,440 --> 00:30:25,160
Go collect these few.

448
00:30:25,799 --> 00:30:26,279
Yes.

449
00:30:28,160 --> 00:30:28,960
Alright boys,

450
00:30:30,640 --> 00:30:31,279
collect the money.

451
00:30:36,759 --> 00:30:38,000
How much can you lend me?

452
00:30:39,640 --> 00:30:40,319
A hundred thousand.

453
00:30:44,960 --> 00:30:45,640
Two hundred thousand.

454
00:30:49,039 --> 00:30:50,960
But you have no collateral.

455
00:30:51,880 --> 00:30:53,799
How can I lend you that much?

456
00:30:57,599 --> 00:30:58,319
Uncle Fang,

457
00:30:59,440 --> 00:31:00,440
may I call you that?

458
00:31:10,880 --> 00:31:12,279
Grandma came to see you once.

459
00:31:12,680 --> 00:31:13,920
She said you're a straightforward man.

460
00:31:17,039 --> 00:31:17,880
Your grandmother?

461
00:31:28,680 --> 00:31:29,519
Huang Xuefen.

462
00:31:30,440 --> 00:31:31,799
Ten years ago, you let us

463
00:31:31,799 --> 00:31:32,920
live in the old factory building.

464
00:31:34,680 --> 00:31:35,400
We were the ones

465
00:31:35,400 --> 00:31:36,839
paying rent to cover the loan.

466
00:31:47,319 --> 00:31:49,119
Huang Xuefen is your grandmother?

467
00:31:52,599 --> 00:31:54,279
She was a formidable woman.

468
00:31:54,680 --> 00:31:55,720
I remember her well.

469
00:31:57,119 --> 00:31:57,960
Back then,

470
00:31:58,640 --> 00:31:59,279
before I'd made

471
00:31:59,279 --> 00:32:00,839
any real success for myself,

472
00:32:01,440 --> 00:32:02,960
she gave me a meal when I had nothing.

473
00:32:03,599 --> 00:32:04,920
That's why I let your family

474
00:32:04,920 --> 00:32:05,839
keep the place

475
00:32:05,839 --> 00:32:07,039
all those years.

476
00:32:10,319 --> 00:32:11,359
You're a man of honor.

477
00:32:12,319 --> 00:32:13,799
My grandmother and I keep our word too.

478
00:32:15,119 --> 00:32:16,640
I wouldn't come to you again

479
00:32:17,720 --> 00:32:19,759
if I wasn't truly desperate.

480
00:32:28,000 --> 00:32:28,640
Fine.

481
00:32:29,960 --> 00:32:31,880
I'll lend you the amount you asked for.

482
00:32:32,200 --> 00:32:33,359
But think this over carefully.

483
00:32:33,480 --> 00:32:35,240
And bring the signed contract back to me.

484
00:32:35,519 --> 00:32:36,640
I owe Mrs. Huang

485
00:32:36,720 --> 00:32:37,839
this favor.

486
00:33:19,559 --> 00:33:20,359
Right, Ms. Chen,

487
00:33:20,720 --> 00:33:21,960
where's my drawing?

488
00:33:22,920 --> 00:33:24,599
Xixiao saw it the other day.

489
00:33:24,599 --> 00:33:25,720
I asked if he wanted it,

490
00:33:25,720 --> 00:33:27,279
he just took it without a word.

491
00:33:27,559 --> 00:33:28,319
He saw it?

492
00:33:40,240 --> 00:33:40,960
Where are you off to?

493
00:33:46,359 --> 00:33:47,759
Grandma's not doing well.

494
00:33:48,480 --> 00:33:50,000
I need to go home for a few days.

495
00:33:52,440 --> 00:33:53,480
I thought she was still hospitalized?

496
00:33:55,119 --> 00:33:56,039
She's been discharged.

497
00:33:57,400 --> 00:33:58,680
While she's not doing well?

498
00:34:03,960 --> 00:34:05,079
Did I say you could leave?

499
00:34:10,199 --> 00:34:12,000
I just don't wanna stay here anymore, okay?

500
00:34:15,199 --> 00:34:15,960
That's not like you.

501
00:34:17,760 --> 00:34:19,239
You're giving up this easily?

502
00:34:22,000 --> 00:34:23,480
Don't you wanna be my family anymore?

503
00:34:26,079 --> 00:34:27,760
Or keep currying favor with me?

504
00:34:30,880 --> 00:34:32,480
You already know everything, don't you?

505
00:34:39,480 --> 00:34:40,880
There's still stuff I don't know.

506
00:34:45,119 --> 00:34:46,239
You can tell me.

507
00:34:48,199 --> 00:34:49,440
If you say it yourself,

508
00:34:49,440 --> 00:34:50,599
I won't blame you.

509
00:34:55,239 --> 00:34:56,760
I've said all I need to say.

510
00:35:28,360 --> 00:35:29,159
Hey beautiful,

511
00:35:30,760 --> 00:35:31,679
I've been calling you but no answer.

512
00:35:31,679 --> 00:35:32,480
What's going on?

513
00:35:33,199 --> 00:35:34,079
The boss wants to know

514
00:35:34,440 --> 00:35:35,199
your answer.

515
00:35:35,519 --> 00:35:36,960
I'll tell you when I've decided.

516
00:35:37,320 --> 00:35:38,440
Zhou Wan, listen.

517
00:35:38,599 --> 00:35:40,800
You're not the one in control here.

518
00:35:41,840 --> 00:35:42,519
Tomorrow.

519
00:35:43,039 --> 00:35:44,079
I need your answer tomorrow.

520
00:35:44,079 --> 00:35:44,800
Got it?

521
00:35:45,440 --> 00:35:46,079
Zhou Wan.

522
00:35:47,639 --> 00:35:48,400
Zhou Wan.

523
00:35:50,400 --> 00:35:50,800
I can't wait to see

524
00:35:50,800 --> 00:35:52,360
what happens

525
00:35:52,360 --> 00:35:54,079
when I've got you.

526
00:35:54,679 --> 00:35:55,239
You should know...

527
00:35:55,239 --> 00:35:57,400
Luo He, itching for another beating?

528
00:35:58,000 --> 00:35:59,559
Watch how you speak.

529
00:35:59,880 --> 00:36:00,360
Lu Xixiao.

530
00:36:00,360 --> 00:36:01,440
Are you out of your mind?

531
00:36:01,440 --> 00:36:02,480
Why do you pop up everywhere?

532
00:36:02,480 --> 00:36:03,360
Stalker.

533
00:36:04,039 --> 00:36:04,920
Look,

534
00:36:05,039 --> 00:36:07,239
I didn't start anything this time.

535
00:36:07,599 --> 00:36:09,079
He's just here to collect rent.

536
00:36:09,639 --> 00:36:10,679
I'm heading back to work now.

537
00:36:13,599 --> 00:36:14,280
Running from me?

538
00:36:15,920 --> 00:36:16,440
I'm not.

539
00:36:16,440 --> 00:36:18,239
I'll be late for my shift.

540
00:36:22,880 --> 00:36:23,559
"Running from me?"

541
00:36:23,719 --> 00:36:24,559
Stalker.

542
00:36:26,199 --> 00:36:27,159
What do you want with her?

543
00:36:33,199 --> 00:36:34,079
Wanna know?

544
00:36:36,559 --> 00:36:37,719
None of your business.

545
00:36:47,159 --> 00:36:48,679
If you really wanna know,

546
00:36:49,159 --> 00:36:50,519
you'll have to pay a price.

547
00:36:54,559 --> 00:36:55,679
You dare make demands of me?

548
00:36:57,199 --> 00:36:58,400
So no deal then?

549
00:37:01,000 --> 00:37:01,719
Fine.

550
00:37:04,519 --> 00:37:05,840
Let's make a bet.

551
00:37:06,400 --> 00:37:07,239
Name the game.

552
00:37:08,039 --> 00:37:08,960
If I win, you tell me everything.

553
00:37:09,480 --> 00:37:10,400
If I lose,

554
00:37:11,119 --> 00:37:12,199
I'll do anything you ask.

555
00:37:14,800 --> 00:37:15,679
Don't back out.

556
00:37:18,599 --> 00:37:20,760
Go, go, go!

557
00:37:23,079 --> 00:37:23,679
Come on!

558
00:37:24,360 --> 00:37:25,519
What're you staring at, kid?

559
00:37:26,480 --> 00:37:26,960
Take him down!

560
00:37:34,480 --> 00:37:35,119
Score!

561
00:37:36,119 --> 00:37:36,800
Nice shot!

562
00:37:37,119 --> 00:37:37,920
Nice shot!

563
00:37:39,559 --> 00:37:40,639
Go, go, go!

564
00:37:47,920 --> 00:37:48,880
Cut the games, a fight

565
00:37:49,480 --> 00:37:50,760
broke out by the basketball court.

566
00:37:50,840 --> 00:37:51,159
Who's fighting?

567
00:37:51,159 --> 00:37:52,000
Luo He and Lu Xixiao.

568
00:37:52,000 --> 00:37:52,679
Basketball match.

569
00:37:52,679 --> 00:37:53,679
Luo He's just playing dirty.

570
00:37:53,679 --> 00:37:55,719
Yeah, let's go check it out.

571
00:37:55,960 --> 00:37:56,760
Okay, let's go.

572
00:38:04,360 --> 00:38:05,039
Can I leave early?

573
00:38:05,039 --> 00:38:05,480
Go ahead.

574
00:38:05,800 --> 00:38:06,480
Don't rush.

575
00:38:07,599 --> 00:38:10,719
Come on, come on, come on!

576
00:38:10,719 --> 00:38:11,880
Foul!

577
00:38:12,360 --> 00:38:15,760
Come on, come on, come on!

578
00:38:18,079 --> 00:38:18,559
Wait.

579
00:38:18,559 --> 00:38:19,760
What?

580
00:38:19,760 --> 00:38:21,599
What? Foul?

581
00:38:21,719 --> 00:38:24,119
No way. Where's the foul?

582
00:38:24,679 --> 00:38:25,960
Come on, come on!

583
00:38:26,840 --> 00:38:33,360
Come on, come on!

584
00:38:42,840 --> 00:38:43,880
How's that not a foul?

585
00:38:47,880 --> 00:38:48,639
Hey!

586
00:38:49,719 --> 00:38:50,519
You okay, Ping?

587
00:38:50,639 --> 00:38:51,280
Yeah, fine.

588
00:38:51,280 --> 00:38:52,360
Uncle.

589
00:38:53,559 --> 00:38:54,519
You all right, Ping?

590
00:38:55,199 --> 00:38:55,920
- I can't go on anymore.
- You hurt?

591
00:38:55,920 --> 00:38:56,679
That's a dirty play!

592
00:38:56,880 --> 00:38:58,039
No call on that?

593
00:38:59,199 --> 00:39:00,239
That's how you play ball?

594
00:39:00,239 --> 00:39:01,000
It's fine.

595
00:39:01,320 --> 00:39:02,000
Is that all you've got?

596
00:39:04,039 --> 00:39:05,000
We're here to play ball.

597
00:39:05,800 --> 00:39:06,400
Focus on the game first.

598
00:39:06,400 --> 00:39:07,280
We'll sort this out later.

599
00:39:10,199 --> 00:39:10,800
Come on!

600
00:39:10,920 --> 00:39:13,480
Come on!

601
00:39:14,480 --> 00:39:16,880
Come on!

602
00:39:17,119 --> 00:39:18,360
Bring it!

603
00:39:20,360 --> 00:39:22,119
Nice one, Jiang Fan!

604
00:39:46,280 --> 00:39:47,559
First half's over.

605
00:39:52,400 --> 00:39:53,079
Second half,

606
00:39:53,559 --> 00:39:55,079
I'm gonna destroy Lu Xixiao.

607
00:39:58,119 --> 00:39:59,280
What should I drink?

608
00:40:02,639 --> 00:40:03,199
This one.

609
00:40:08,840 --> 00:40:09,760
Look who it is.

610
00:40:09,760 --> 00:40:11,360
Our leading lady.

611
00:40:16,880 --> 00:40:17,920
Play nicely.

612
00:40:17,920 --> 00:40:19,039
No cheap shots.

613
00:40:19,480 --> 00:40:21,320
Me, cheap? How so?

614
00:40:22,119 --> 00:40:23,960
I just don't like you.

615
00:40:23,960 --> 00:40:24,719
And I hate

616
00:40:24,719 --> 00:40:26,079
Lu Xixiao all the same.

617
00:40:26,360 --> 00:40:28,519
I'll make both of you miserable,

618
00:40:28,519 --> 00:40:30,000
mark my words.

619
00:40:32,239 --> 00:40:33,559
Why'd he agree to play you?

620
00:40:34,519 --> 00:40:35,239
Wanna know?

621
00:40:37,960 --> 00:40:39,280
None of your business.

622
00:40:41,760 --> 00:40:42,400
Zhou Wan.

623
00:40:43,159 --> 00:40:44,079
You know what?

624
00:40:44,079 --> 00:40:45,679
You're actually really pretty.

625
00:40:48,960 --> 00:40:49,760
Don't touch me.

626
00:40:52,159 --> 00:40:54,840
You little vixen, you've totally got

627
00:40:55,840 --> 00:40:57,559
Lu Xixiao wrapped around your finger.

628
00:41:02,239 --> 00:41:03,280
All you can say

629
00:41:03,400 --> 00:41:04,840
is gross garbage.

630
00:41:06,559 --> 00:41:07,360
Zhou Wan.

631
00:41:08,079 --> 00:41:09,280
Don't forget.

632
00:41:09,480 --> 00:41:11,079
Your Grandma's life is in my hands.

633
00:41:11,320 --> 00:41:12,000
I didn't forget.

634
00:41:14,159 --> 00:41:15,280
I just feel sorry for you.

635
00:41:16,559 --> 00:41:17,320
Because you'll never

636
00:41:17,320 --> 00:41:18,519
beat Lu Xixiao.

637
00:41:19,760 --> 00:41:20,840
You go through all this trouble

638
00:41:20,840 --> 00:41:21,519
just to beat him once

639
00:41:21,519 --> 00:41:23,159
on a tiny basketball court.

640
00:41:23,920 --> 00:41:24,760
But even if you win,

641
00:41:24,760 --> 00:41:25,920
you won't win fair.

642
00:41:26,800 --> 00:41:28,599
Everyone'll snicker behind your back,

643
00:41:29,000 --> 00:41:29,960
look down on you.

644
00:41:31,719 --> 00:41:32,199
You think

645
00:41:32,199 --> 00:41:32,760
I won't hit a girl?

646
00:41:32,760 --> 00:41:33,880
Chill, bro, come on.

647
00:41:34,039 --> 00:41:34,599
Back off!

648
00:41:35,400 --> 00:41:36,000
Is that so?

649
00:41:36,639 --> 00:41:37,519
I don't think that at all.

650
00:41:38,719 --> 00:41:40,360
Hitting girls is just what you do.

651
00:41:45,400 --> 00:41:46,480
Bro, bro, bro.

652
00:41:46,480 --> 00:41:47,119
Easy, easy.

653
00:41:47,559 --> 00:41:48,480
Come on, bro.

654
00:41:48,800 --> 00:41:50,039
What did you say? Say it again.

655
00:41:50,880 --> 00:41:51,920
Am I scared of him?

656
00:41:51,920 --> 00:41:52,559
You're not.

657
00:41:52,559 --> 00:41:53,119
Am I?

658
00:41:53,119 --> 00:41:54,000
Not one bit.

